<p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744369358029.png" alt="1744369358029.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744369358029.png" style="width: 648.42px;height: 410.12px;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">工整严谨的笔记，是思想的沉淀，更是信仰的印记。为扎实推进理论学习，发挥榜样引领作用，本期“每月一评”活动精选出四份优秀纸质笔记，这些笔记清晰地展现了经济管理学院第32期入党积极分子的学习风采。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">B230507杨文莹</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744369484474.jpg" alt="1744369484474.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744369484474.jpg" style="width: 551.00px;height: 836.60px;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">B230507谢俐俐</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744369469828.jpg" alt="1744369469828.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744369469828.jpg" style="width: 558.42px;height: 744.56px;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">B230502黄梦昕</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744369893048.jpg" alt="1744369893048.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744369893048.jpg" style="width: 563.42px;height: 803.92px;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">B230501 王乐熙</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744370027392.jpg" alt="1744370027392.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744370027392.jpg" style="width: 573.42px;height: 764.56px;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">笔记是学习过程的记录，更是成长进步的见证。入党积极分子们以纸笔为媒介，用心沉淀每一次感悟，用热忱镌刻每一次收获。在今后的日子里，让我们紧握手中笔，书写对党忠诚、无悔人生的青春华章。</span></p><p><br></p>